{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d43717d54e","title":"关于同国民党谈判及军事部署致潘汉年、叶剑英电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9f8039f7ab","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":10,"articleId":"d43717d54e"}],"tags":[{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"35a54080cd","type":"paragraph","text":"关于同国民党谈判及军事部署","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"3738ef2099","type":"paragraph","text":"致潘汉年、叶剑英电","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"1623e5d110","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月10日）开、剑：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"b69e9dac02","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、张子华二十日到广州，二十八日发一来电，九日收到。据称，陈立夫赴宁数日可回，见了曾养甫，约恩来飞赴香港或广州会谈，我们复，先停战后谈判，看其复电如何再说。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"94aaf68ac1","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、二方面军外翼已不利，决集内线，朱、张已到大道","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"ca29d52038","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、为执行尔后战略行动之便利，须设法使王以哲驻固原指挥，将何柱国南调，可借二方面军北进调换之","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"185965fbcb","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、毅兄“主力宜集平凉，在固原不宜置多兵，蒋即有意调固原两师尚南，宜即执行于我有利","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"29578ad53b","type":"paragraph","text":"戊、抗胡、侯二方面军到通渭后再部署，兄等设法推延时间。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"16820ebf5f","type":"paragraph","text":"东","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"},{"id":"113d83f709","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十日十时[1]指张学良。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e"}],"page":{"id":"69c30a0379","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d43717d54e","start":213,"end":213}}}},"__N_SSG":true}